CT
Safe
App
Effective Date: 06/13/2024
Introduction
Welcome to the CT
Safe
App, operated by Tyler Technologies. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and share information when you use our app.
Information We Collect
The CT
Safe
App only collects the following personal information from you:
Name
Email address
Phone number
You have the option to toggle this information on or off within the app settings.
Use of Information
The primary purpose of collecting your personal information is to facilitate the sending of Suspicious Activity Reports (SARs). These reports can include:
A description of the suspicious activity
Location data
An image
You are not required to send any information if you choose not to.
Sharing of Information
Our server does not store any personal information from users. Instead, it directly forwards any submitted reports to the third party, the State of Connecticut Division of Emergency Services and Public Protection (DESPP), Division of Emergency Management and Homeland Security (DEMHS). We do not retain any copies of your data.
Third-Party Privacy Policy
The use of the CT
Safe
App is also subject to the Connecticut Intelligence Center Privacy, Civil Rights, and Civil Liberties Protection Policy. This policy ensures compliance with applicable laws concerning the submission of Suspicious Activity Reports. The purpose of this policy is to protect individual privacy, civil rights, civil liberties, and other protected interests while enhancing public safety and national security.
Your Choices
Toggle Information:
You can choose to toggle your personal information on or off in the app settings at any time.
Submit Reports:
You are not obligated to submit any information through the app. The submission of reports is entirely voluntary.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the CT
Safe
App, please contact us at
https://ctinteractive.zendesk.com/hc/en-us
.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.